room_title: Escape room "Save the Queen" by Team vs Time in Hartford
room_description: You and your companions will experience the Dark Ages like never before! As members of the royal court, you will travel to 14th-century England, where you have unearthed a diabolical plot by a cabal of errant knights bent on unseating the Queen. Your quest is to uncover the clues, escape the chamber, and alert the court before they succeed in their insurrection.
